name: Lurking Between the Trees 1
description:
Lurking Between the Trees 1 is the first piece in the series Lurking Between the Trees. It is the genesis NFT of the artist Magic Mountain Fairy.

The series consists of 20 pieces and was co-created using a neural network.
It shows (mostly) hidden creatures, far from civilization, embedded deeply in the forest.

Resolution: 4096 × 4096 px
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mmountainfairy
